00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:01:05,952 --> 00:01:08,384
=No Doubt In Us=
(Adapted from the Manman comic No Doubt in Us)

2
00:01:08,512 --> 00:01:11,424
=Episode 19=

3
00:01:22,959 --> 00:01:24,200
Greetings, Queen of Dada.

4
00:01:25,920 --> 00:01:27,159
Please be seated.

5
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:33,680
What brings you here?

6
00:01:34,239 --> 00:01:38,000
We seek to collaborate with you
to overthrow the imperial power.

7
00:01:38,319 --> 00:01:41,400
This would be a great benefit for Dada.

8
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:43,799
Previously, you conspired
with my brother to harm me.

9
00:01:44,480 --> 00:01:46,000
And now you want to cooperate with me?

10
00:01:46,799 --> 00:01:49,000
Do you take us for fools?

11
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:54,680
My father promised to offer your brother
three cities after seizing the throne.

12
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:56,480
I offer five cities.

13
00:01:58,200 --> 00:02:00,319
My father has petitioned to retire
due to illness.

14
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:04,000
His Majesty has approved his petition,
and I now handle affairs in his stead.

15
00:02:04,519 --> 00:02:05,719
Currently,

16
00:02:06,879 --> 00:02:08,080
I'm in charge.

17
00:02:12,599 --> 00:02:14,039
It's indeed a good offer.

18
00:02:14,639 --> 00:02:17,120
Unfortunately, I am not interested.

19
00:02:18,879 --> 00:02:20,080
You may take your leave.

20
00:02:22,080 --> 00:02:24,120
What if I offer five more cities?

21
00:02:24,479 --> 00:02:26,199
You are well-learned.

22
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:28,159
You must have heard this saying.

23
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:30,639
"How can a square peg fit a round hole?

24
00:02:30,719 --> 00:02:32,520
How can
those on different paths coexist?"

25
00:02:34,599 --> 00:02:37,400
I didn't expect you
to be so well-versed in literature.

26
00:02:37,719 --> 00:02:42,599
In that case,
you may state any additional demands.

27
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:45,639
Dada is remote, with scant troops.

28
00:02:46,039 --> 00:02:47,599
Therefore, every citizen is a soldier.

29
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:49,472
But it's just to defend our homeland.

30
00:02:49,719 --> 00:02:51,479
We hope for peace.

31
00:02:52,520 --> 00:02:53,240
Yet you

32
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:58,680
seek to exploit Dada to restart the war
and help you seize the throne.

33
00:02:59,599 --> 00:03:01,520
I can also bring you peace.

34
00:03:03,840 --> 00:03:06,520
You don't bring peace.
You just grant peace.

35
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:09,840
I do not trust you.

36
00:03:17,360 --> 00:03:18,599
Finally caught you.

37
00:03:19,319 --> 00:03:21,520
Huna did meet with Xiao Jinle.

38
00:03:22,479 --> 00:03:23,560
I must let Jinyun know.

39
00:03:25,159 --> 00:03:26,039
Jinming.

40
00:03:27,759 --> 00:03:30,960
What a coincidence meeting you here!

41
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:35,719
Would you like me
to show you around the capital?

42
00:03:36,080 --> 00:03:36,639
No need.

43
00:03:37,199 --> 00:03:37,719
However,

44
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:40,520
I hope you can pass a message
to your brother.

45
00:03:44,759 --> 00:03:45,259
One.

46
00:03:46,479 --> 00:03:46,979
Two.

47
00:03:48,479 --> 00:03:49,000
One.

48
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:51,060
Two.

49
00:03:52,599 --> 00:03:53,120
Hard!

50
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:55,759
Hold on!

51
00:03:58,199 --> 00:04:01,439
I've reviewed your medical records.
Each of you is exceptionally frail.

52
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:04,759
Martial training
can strengthen your body.

53
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:08,680
Your Majesty, we are imperial consorts.

54
00:04:08,719 --> 00:04:10,319
We serve His Majesty.

55
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:13,240
How can we possibly
manage martial training?

56
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:15,680
Her Majesty is right.

57
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:18,600
To serve His Majesty,
we must be physically fit.

58
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:23,040
I find Your Majesty is
particularly reasonable.

59
00:04:24,319 --> 00:04:26,800
I learned it
after watching it just once.

60
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,100
Look.

61
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:30,060
One.

62
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:31,980
Two.

63
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:34,920
Well done, but...

64
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,120
Look.

65
00:04:39,079 --> 00:04:40,899
Exert a force on the waist.

66
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:46,639
Tighten up.

67
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:51,639
Well done.

68
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:55,639
Look, all of you learn
from Consort Zhao.

69
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:58,519
Well done, Consort Zhao. Take a break.

70
00:05:00,199 --> 00:05:00,699
Yes.

71
00:05:01,839 --> 00:05:03,959
I had Xuan prepare cooling tea
for everyone.

72
00:05:04,839 --> 00:05:06,000
Everyone, come have some.

73
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:21,600
This is delicious.

74
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,839
I love it, Your Majesty.

75
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:25,240
We've worked so hard.

76
00:05:25,399 --> 00:05:26,839
Yet we only have a cup of green tea.

77
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:30,360
Only when parched
does one know water's sweetness.

78
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:32,959
Only when starving
does one know rice's fragrance.

79
00:05:33,199 --> 00:05:34,959
The hardship you endure now

80
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:37,120
lays the foundation for your future.

81
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:39,040
Her Majesty is right.

82
00:05:42,959 --> 00:05:44,720
Huna, what brings you here?

83
00:05:46,439 --> 00:05:49,639
Those who exercise have firm muscles
and move agilely.

84
00:05:49,959 --> 00:05:53,160
They're less likely to get sick
and remain composed in danger.

85
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:56,240
Knowing some martial arts
is better than being at others' mercy.

86
00:05:59,079 --> 00:06:02,199
I'm returning home tomorrow.
I came specifically to bid you farewell.

87
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:04,160
You're leaving tomorrow?

88
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:09,000
In Dada, every citizen is a soldier.

89
00:06:09,439 --> 00:06:11,560
Even my handmaids
can kill wolves barehanded.

90
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:14,439
You should be grateful
that you have a good Empress.

91
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:16,879
Otherwise,
when armies besiege your city,

92
00:06:17,199 --> 00:06:18,680
you will be helpless.

93
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:23,319
Let's spar again.

94
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:29,519
That's all for today.
You may go back and rest.

95
00:06:30,660 --> 00:06:31,160
Let's go.

96
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:31,660
Let's go.

97
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:32,540
No need.

98
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:37,079
Your Majesty.

99
00:06:38,839 --> 00:06:39,879
Go ahead.

100
00:06:40,439 --> 00:06:43,800
I will ensure they practice diligently

101
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:46,680
and never give up.

102
00:06:47,079 --> 00:06:49,920
You will continue? That's very good.

103
00:06:53,879 --> 00:06:54,379
Let's go.

104
00:07:02,319 --> 00:07:05,000
It's been so long since I met someone
who can ride horses with me.

105
00:07:05,879 --> 00:07:07,680
Riding and shooting arrows with you

106
00:07:07,879 --> 00:07:10,560
reminded me of our days fighting
against the enemy in Dada.

107
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:12,639
But I feel you've improved

108
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:14,279
since then.

109
00:07:14,639 --> 00:07:17,160
Our people are skilled at riding
and shooting arrows.

110
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:19,480
I am the Queen,
so naturally, I'm even more skilled.

111
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:23,759
What is this?

112
00:07:23,959 --> 00:07:24,459
A gift.

113
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:45,720
This is...

114
00:07:46,319 --> 00:07:48,759
Its name is Aqi. It's a gift for you.

115
00:07:49,399 --> 00:07:50,360
When you need me,

116
00:07:50,879 --> 00:07:52,920
no matter where I am, Aqi can find me.

117
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:54,000
Really?

118
00:07:55,079 --> 00:07:56,199
Aqi.

119
00:07:56,319 --> 00:07:58,000
Next spring,

120
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:58,959
come to Dada.

121
00:07:59,399 --> 00:08:02,360
The tastiest meat, the strongest liquor,
and the fastest horse

122
00:08:02,759 --> 00:08:03,519
will be yours.

123
00:08:05,079 --> 00:08:07,560
I will keep my promise.
No matter how far, I will come to you.

124
00:08:08,279 --> 00:08:09,199
See you then.

125
00:08:10,439 --> 00:08:14,120
Aqi, so cute!

126
00:08:14,519 --> 00:08:17,360
Aqi, my name is Xu Yu.

127
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:23,759
Wintersweet blooms in snow.
The stove fire warms a cold night.

128
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:28,519
This is Huna's riddle.

129
00:08:29,439 --> 00:08:30,319
Yes, Jinyun.

130
00:08:30,839 --> 00:08:33,600
Huna is quite cunning and scheming.

131
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:36,639
I fear their meeting today
was to plan something.

132
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:37,919
About what?

133
00:08:38,799 --> 00:08:39,440
Xu Yu.

134
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:42,340
Try these.

135
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:45,039
Xu Yu, you know what?

136
00:08:45,639 --> 00:08:48,039
Today I saw Xiao Jinle meeting
with Huna.

137
00:08:48,279 --> 00:08:49,559
They talked for a long time.

138
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:53,000
Xiao Jinle allied with her brother
to seize her throne.

139
00:08:53,559 --> 00:08:55,360
How could she possibly
cooperate with him?

140
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:57,879
Besides, I trust Huna.

141
00:08:58,399 --> 00:08:59,600
Being wary matters.

142
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:02,679
But I feel the truth may not be so.

143
00:09:03,399 --> 00:09:06,080
Otherwise, Huna
wouldn't have left you this riddle.

144
00:09:06,799 --> 00:09:07,720
What riddle?

145
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:09,440
I know.

146
00:09:09,919 --> 00:09:12,679
Wintersweet blooms in snow.
The stove fire warms a cold night.

147
00:09:13,399 --> 00:09:14,000
Right?

148
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:24,120
Huna, did you enjoy your time in Chen?

149
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:26,240
Your Majesty sends me off so early.

150
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:27,776
It seems you truly dislike me.

151
00:09:28,544 --> 00:09:31,200
Your Majesty, are you afraid
that I will steal your Empress?

152
00:09:32,559 --> 00:09:35,720
Of course not. I should thank you.

153
00:09:36,399 --> 00:09:37,799
After all, because of your arrival,

154
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:39,639
I've become determined.

155
00:09:40,399 --> 00:09:42,120
I'll devote myself wholeheartedly
to Xu Yu.

156
00:09:42,679 --> 00:09:45,279
I won't give anyone an opportunity.

157
00:09:45,799 --> 00:09:48,000
Good luck then, Your Majesty.

158
00:09:58,320 --> 00:10:00,240
It's getting late.
Take care, Your Majesty.

159
00:10:02,519 --> 00:10:03,320
Take care.

160
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:08,080
Huna.

161
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:31,679
This is for you.

162
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:34,840
You're skilled with scimitars
and surely like this.

163
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:36,864
Thank you. I like it very much.

164
00:10:37,280 --> 00:10:38,320
That's good.

165
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:44,519
Remember our promise.
I'll wait for you in Dada.

166
00:10:49,759 --> 00:10:50,639
I'll miss you.

167
00:11:08,679 --> 00:11:09,559
Safe journey!

168
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:27,279
Goodbye, Huna.

169
00:11:34,039 --> 00:11:37,600
I often wonder
what it feels like to drink

170
00:11:37,759 --> 00:11:39,080
and ride freely in the desert.

171
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:44,240
Could you describe that feeling

172
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:46,000
to me in detail?

173
00:11:46,879 --> 00:11:48,759
Hearing others describe is boring.

174
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:50,320
Your Majesty should feel it yourself.

175
00:11:50,559 --> 00:11:52,200
I can escort you there. What do you say?

176
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:55,960
Okay. Next spring,

177
00:11:56,159 --> 00:11:58,679
I will definitely travel there.

178
00:12:01,274 --> 00:12:02,399
(Tea)

179
00:12:02,399 --> 00:12:04,919
I wonder why you have asked me to come.

180
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:07,399
Jinyun and Xu Yu
once switched their bodies.

181
00:12:08,320 --> 00:12:09,799
You must be aware of it.

182
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:12,080
Last time, I made myself very clear.

183
00:12:12,919 --> 00:12:13,879
I do not trust you.

184
00:12:14,559 --> 00:12:16,000
So naturally, we won't cooperate.

185
00:12:17,159 --> 00:12:20,600
(She's so calm,
so she must have known long ago.)

186
00:12:21,639 --> 00:12:23,240
Follow your heart and ask yourself.

187
00:12:23,639 --> 00:12:26,799
Will the Emperor's promise
remain forever unchanged?

188
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:29,200
Can the contract last forever unbroken?

189
00:12:31,399 --> 00:12:33,799
If you have even a trace of doubt,

190
00:12:34,440 --> 00:12:36,200
please hedge your bets.

191
00:12:36,879 --> 00:12:38,799
It might not be a bad choice.

192
00:12:39,639 --> 00:12:43,639
All we want is Dada's cooperation
on the border.

193
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:47,559
For you, it would be effortless.

194
00:12:50,399 --> 00:12:50,919
Alright.

195
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:54,200
I will consider it carefully.

196
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:11,720
(Presented to Princess's Palace)
You submitted 318 memorials,

197
00:13:12,080 --> 00:13:13,639
all urging me to have an heir.

198
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:16,360
Do you think

199
00:13:17,039 --> 00:13:18,120
I won't punish you all?

200
00:13:19,120 --> 00:13:22,000
Your Majesty, it's the people's will.

201
00:13:22,039 --> 00:13:25,080
Moreover, Your Majesty has been married
to Her Majesty for years.

202
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:26,360
Yet she has not conceived.

203
00:13:26,519 --> 00:13:29,960
Such a thing has never occurred
in Chen before.

204
00:13:30,480 --> 00:13:32,480
We are anxious and worried.

205
00:13:32,679 --> 00:13:34,559
We hope Your Majesty will understand.

206
00:13:34,919 --> 00:13:38,399
Jinle, you are my cousin.

207
00:13:38,799 --> 00:13:40,679
Will you also
meddle in my private affairs?

208
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:44,600
As your liege, I know the boundaries.

209
00:13:44,960 --> 00:13:46,320
I have only two wishes.

210
00:13:46,799 --> 00:13:49,919
Your Majesty will have children,
and our nation will become prosperous.

211
00:13:51,919 --> 00:13:53,639
Well said!

212
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:57,000
I've heard that Your Majesty
often stays in Fengyi Palace

213
00:13:57,000 --> 00:13:58,879
and rarely sees other concubines.

214
00:13:59,159 --> 00:14:01,399
This is probably improper, isn't it?

215
00:14:01,879 --> 00:14:03,519
Your Majesty is the ruler of the nation.

216
00:14:04,279 --> 00:14:08,320
How can you value your romantic love
over offspring?

217
00:14:10,639 --> 00:14:14,360
Are you going
to control which woman I see?

218
00:14:14,840 --> 00:14:16,720
However, we heard

219
00:14:16,840 --> 00:14:19,039
Her Majesty has never conceived.

220
00:14:19,159 --> 00:14:20,320
We are deeply concerned.

221
00:14:20,720 --> 00:14:22,799
Her Majesty
has difficulty having children.

222
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:23,759
How dare you!

223
00:14:25,840 --> 00:14:28,080
How dare you judge Her Majesty!

224
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:30,799
Your Majesty,
a woman who cannot bear children

225
00:14:31,039 --> 00:14:33,879
is considered an ill omen
even among the common people.

226
00:14:34,159 --> 00:14:36,279
How much more so
for the Empress of a nation?

227
00:14:36,840 --> 00:14:38,559
I beg Your Majesty

228
00:14:38,720 --> 00:14:42,200
to restart the concubine selection,
as the imperial lineage is paramount.

229
00:14:42,879 --> 00:14:46,240
Otherwise, you should
appoint a better person as the Empress.

230
00:14:49,559 --> 00:14:51,600
- We beg you, Your Majesty,
- We beg you, Your Majesty,

231
00:14:51,600 --> 00:14:55,399
- to put the nation first
- to put the nation first

232
00:14:55,679 --> 00:14:58,559
- and continue the imperial lineage.
- and continue the imperial lineage.

233
00:15:17,274 --> 00:15:22,458
♪Parting clouds
to pluck the waxing moon♪

234
00:15:23,194 --> 00:15:27,757
♪Brewing a pot of bygone years♪

235
00:15:29,082 --> 00:15:34,497
♪Chill flame, window shade,
console my grieving soul♪

236
00:15:35,066 --> 00:15:39,610
♪Drunk through lifetimes
with no dreams returned♪

237
00:15:40,250 --> 00:15:45,514
♪If not for letting go, how could I
bear to shatter this dream♪

238
00:15:45,882 --> 00:15:51,559
♪Returning to drift
through the mortal world♪

239
00:15:51,898 --> 00:15:53,914
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

240
00:15:54,106 --> 00:15:57,850
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

241
00:15:58,426 --> 00:16:03,098
♪Fate laid bare my deepest thoughts♪

242
00:16:03,642 --> 00:16:05,402
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

243
00:16:05,722 --> 00:16:09,338
♪Loving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting♪

244
00:16:09,585 --> 00:16:15,112
♪Tell me, after all this entanglement,
who regrets it more♪

